      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six masterpiece. The engine features individual throttle bodies providing exceptional transient response, while the VANOS system and rod bearings have been addressed to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry that preserves its legendary 50/50 weight distribution. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a mechanical limited-slip differential, offering a tactile, analog driving experience. While it displays the honest aesthetic wear of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its structural and mechanical integrity makes it an ideal candidate for the purist who prioritizes performance and handling dynamics over a showroom-static life.",
      "price": 36500.0,
