      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 luxury SUV that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you'll find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway commuting. Inside, the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; the engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership, with a full folder of records available for your review. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires and a complete brake fluid flush. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine respect and consistent care.",
